Mario Fabrizi https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mario_Fabrizi 0 Mario E.P. Fabrizi (1924 – 5 April 1963) was an English comedian and actor of Italian descent, noted for his luxuriant moustache, active in Britain in the 1950s and early 1960s.
